    <string name="help_how_to_play_header">💧 How to play?</string>
    <string name="help_how_to_play_text">
        1. <b>Choose your challenge:</b>\n
            Begin selecting your difficulty: 6x6, 8x8, or 10x10. This defines the size of the board and the number of ships.\n
        2. <b>Explore the ocean:</b>\n
            If it\'s not a ship, you\'re just floating!.\n
        3. <b>Battle report:</b>\n
           • <font color='#FF9800'><b>HIT!</b></font> (🛳): You just found a ship! Continue exploring the board.\n
           • <font color='#03A9F4'><b>SPLASH!</b></font> (🌊): There was just water. Adjust your aim and keep trying!\n
    </string>
